channel.title: How to make an area non wild?
channel.description:
Me and my friend are trying to make a modisland and adminisland and we found both places, but they are both wild. Thing is, neither of us know how to make it nonwild.
[code]|| (absX >= && absX <= && absY >= && absY <= )[/code]
What does absX, absX, absY and absY stand for?
